main event: UFO report related to Project Blue Book from May 19, 1967, in Lexington, Kentucky.
interesting points: The report includes 4 black and white photographs of the night sky,The photographs show a starry sky with distinctive star patterns,Some faint dots of light appear in one of the images,One photo indicates a possible moving object with a faint line or trail,No human figures or identifiable objects are visible in any of the photographs.
